│ missing SDKs indicates the cached authentication is invalid                 │
│                                                                             │
│ .                                                                           │
│                                                                             │
│ Multiple recent forum reports show SDK Manager fails to access repositories │
│ when the cached session is stale, even after successful initial login       │
│                                                                             │
│  (https://forums.developer.nvidia.com/t/sdk-manager-says-no-permission-to-a │
