│                                                                             │
│ ## Diagnosis                                                                │
│                                                                             │
│ The log shows a critical failure: **"Read-only file system"** with          │
│ installation aborted at the **postinst** stage. This indicates that during  │
│ the post-installation phase (when the installer was trying to write files   │
│ or modify system permissions/configuration), it encountered a filesystem    │
│ that was mounted as read-only. This is a filesystem-level permission issue, │
│ not an SDK or JetPack-specific problem.                                     │
│                                                                             │
